data.description: Welcome to 501 Windwood on Skye, where luxurious living meets the charm of Fayetteville's premier neighborhood. This magnificent 4-bedroom, 4.5-bathroom estate sprawls over an impressive 4,500 square feet of meticulously designed living space, offering an unparalleled blend of elegance and functionality. Upon entering this opulent residence, you'll immediately appreciate the grandeur that awaits you. The primary bedroom, conveniently located on the main level, is a true oasis of relaxation. Step into the most luxurious bathroom you've ever seen, complete with a generously sized soaking tub and a rejuvenating steam shower. The highlight, however, is the expansive walk-in closet, thoughtfully designed with his and hers sides, ensuring that you have all the space you need for your wardrobe. As you ascend the elegant staircase to the upper level, you'll discover three additional bedrooms, each boasting its own en suite bathroom. Whether it's for family members or guests, this layout offers both privacy and comfort. There's also a bonus room and an office space that provides versatility for your lifestyle needs. For those who appreciate outdoor living, this home has it all. Step into the fenced-in yard, offering a secure and private space for outdoor activities. The deck, accessible from the sunroom, is an entertainer's dream, perfect for hosting gatherings, enjoying your morning coffee, or simply basking in the tranquility of the neighborhood.  Convenience and practicality are not overlooked in this property. A 2-car detached garage with unfinished space above provides ample storage. Furthermore, a 2-car carport leads directly into the mudroom and kitchen, making daily living a breeze. This home is more than just a home; it's a lifestyle. This exquisite property marries the best of Fayetteville's premier neighborhood with the comfort, luxury, and functionality you desire. Don't miss your opportunity to experience the epitome of fine living.
